PSST… I’VE GOT A SECRET TO TELL YA👇🏼.
.
My favorite season is upon us! Aka the season of giving and KRISMAS🎉🎁. I want to give you guys some Black Friday coaching specials a lil EARLY😉.
.
⚡️This deal is for my ladies who⚡️
- Want to change for the better in 2020 but need that accountability to make it happen.
- Want to live a healthy lifestyle but also doesn’t want to give up their social life.
- Are ready to invest in themselves and finally say ✌🏼 to their excuses that held them back in 2019.
.
Does that sound like you?
.
If you’ve ever considered joining the Built + Balanced tribe, either in person or online you now have the opportunity to join while rocking a pair of free AirPods…. Yeah you heard that right🙀.
.
Do you want to feel supported? Empowered? Strong? Educated? There is SO much included in this coaching program but I won’t keep you here all day— let’s get to the deal👇🏼.
.
I have 3 spots available (in-person and online) to sign up and rock a pair of AirPods while you build your confidence both inside + outside the gym💪🏼.
.
If you haven’t heard already, I’m takin my talents down south… AKA to Columbus in less than 10 days. So all my CBUS girls— now is the time👯‍♀️.
.
Interested in making progress before the new year? Interested in feeling your best from the inside out? Drop a 🙋🏼‍♀️ below and I will reach out with details!
.
⚡️This deal will be available from today (11/16) - next Saturday (11/23). These spots are FIRST come FIRST served and once they are claimed— that’s it my friends!
.
.
.
